{
  "chapter": "第三章：代数之美——椭圆标准方程的构建",
  "scenes": [
    {
      "id": "ch03_s07_intro",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": { "expression": "thinking" },
      "dialogue": { "text": "化简到这一步，出现了 a\u00b2\u2212c\u00b2。因为它始终大于 0，我们不妨给它起个新名字。观察黑板上的直角三角形，你能找到它对应的线段吗？" },
      "blackboard": { "type": "image", "src": "/labimage/ch03/triangle_pof2.svg" },
      "next": "ch03_s07_quiz"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s07_quiz",
      "type": "choice",
      "mambo": { "expression": "thinking" },
      "dialogue": { "text": "当 P 在短轴顶点时，a 对应 PF\u2082，c 对应 OF\u2082，那么 \u221a(a\u00b2\u2212c\u00b2) 对应的线段是？" },
      "blackboard": { "type": "image", "src": "/labimage/ch03/triangle_pof2.svg" },
      "options": [
        { "text": "A. PF\u2081", "correct": false, "next": "ch03_s07_wrong" },
        { "text": "B. OF\u2081", "correct": false, "next": "ch03_s07_wrong" },
        { "text": "C. OP（短轴半长）", "correct": true, "next": "ch03_s07_correct", "scoreChange": 10 }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s07_correct",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": { "expression": "happy", "action": "bounce" },
      "dialogue": { "text": "没错！根据勾股定理，我们令 b = \u221a(a\u00b2\u2212c\u00b2)，即 b\u00b2 = a\u00b2\u2212c\u00b2。" },
      "blackboard": { "type": "math", "content": "b = \\sqrt{a^2 - c^2}, \\quad b^2 = a^2 - c^2" },
      "next": "ch03_s07_substitute"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s07_substitute",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": { "expression": "excited" },
      "dialogue": { "text": "把 b\u00b2 = a\u00b2\u2212c\u00b2 代入方程，两边同除以 a\u00b2b\u00b2，看看会发生什么！" },
      "blackboard": { "type": "image", "src": "/labimage/ch03/derivation_final.svg" },
      "next": "ch03_s08_reveal"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s07_wrong",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": { "expression": "sad", "action": "shake" },
      "dialogue": { "text": "再想想，当 P 在短轴顶点时，\u25b3POF\u2082 是直角三角形，OP 是一条直角边，用勾股定理算算看？" },
